{"tid":176732,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［1Q題］有冇人知呢條答案係乜？","createTime":"2017-03-28T11:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T11:27:29.000Z","uid":93890,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4684bc155a47f2078b771179a236229539dda5cb","tid":176732,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"有個FD踢波個陣甩左粒LIN <br />\n話說佢唔著衫踢 <br />\n之後就入左波 <br />\n跟住學D足球員胸貼地咁滑地下 <br />\n點知一滑個下 <br />\n捽甩左粒lin <br />\n我地成班FD見到已經笑到Hi Hi <br />\n咁我地就叫白車啦 <br />\n聽電話個個都笑住問我地係邊到咁 <br />\n之後去到醫院 <br />\n個醫生問粒LIN去左邊 <br />\n我個FD話:粒LIN有用架??唔向左走向右走係呀?? <br />\n粒LIN而家應該仲係球場到 <br />\n咁返去搵已經唔見左 <br />\n我個FD就係咁冇左粒LIN<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n估人名 第三頁開估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5073faca632d0d6126d8fa48e8f6da185c5b41c4","tid":176732,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0df57159d10960e603e8293db877d53d2440d24","tid":176732,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d917402226596549bc1d981d3001228954fb1f","tid":176732,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162a6d54a4eeae32dc461a471cf0a4408eaede95","tid":176732,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ef61400b2ff772f0f3efcec14c5582dd4a31af","tid":176732,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:18:55.000Z","msg":"曹永廉"},{"pid":"a34009a63e2ef39580b9065de85b45cb7dc9d768","tid":176732,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20